3013:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         channels 1 and channel 2 are reserved and cannot be used for other
3014:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         purpose.
